data.chText: 雕塑，雕像，塑像（大小通常等于或大于真人或实物）
data.enText: a figure of a person or an animal in stone, metal, etc., usually the same size as in real life or larger

simple_means.memory_skill: stat 站，立 + ue → 站着的〔雕像〕→ 雕像

means: 塑像(大小通常等于或大于真人或实物)

tr: a sculpture representing a human or animal

value.def: A statue is a large sculpture of a person or an animal, made of stone or metal.
